OL,3,CFamilies speak out about loved ones'
OL,4,Ctreatment as Muckamore report published
OL,6,FFamilies of patients at Muckamore
OL,7,FAbbey have said the consequences of
OL,8,Fthe treatment their loved ones
OL,9,Freceived will never leave them.
OL,11,FThe inquiry report into the Co Antrim
OL,12,Fhospital published on Thursday
OL,13,Fidentified 'serious and sustained
OL,14,Ffailures' in the care and protection
OL,15,Fof vulnerable adults.
OL,17,FPatients were restrained, seclusion
OL,18,Fwas used as a punishment and some were
OL,19,Fheavily medicated to the point they
OL,20,Fwere left 'zombified'.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/6
