PN,41402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1781866972
OL,3,CFamilies speak out about loved ones'
OL,4,Ctreatment as Muckamore report published
OL,6,FWhile the inquiry has exposed how
OL,7,Fwidespread failures were, for some
OL,8,Ffamilies crucial questions remain
OL,9,Funanswered.
OL,11,FDanny Diamond's son Eoin - who has
OL,12,Fsince passed away - spent years in and
OL,13,Fout of Muckamore.
OL,15,FHis father often found him bruised and
OL,16,Flosing weight and feared he was being
OL,17,Fneglected.
OL,19,FEoin left the hospital before the
OL,20,Fabuse scandal came to light.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
