FL,415,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1781866972
OL,3,CFamilies speak out about loved ones'
OL,4,Ctreatment as Muckamore report published
OL,6,FNow, Danny is left wondering what
OL,7,Freally happened behind the hospital's
OL,8,Fdoors.
OL,10,F"To be totally honest, it's a guilt
OL,11,Fthat I have to live with that he was
OL,12,Fever in that place. It's very hard to
OL,13,Flive with.
OL,15,F"The only blessing I have is that Eoin
OL,16,Fwas out of there in a year.
OL,18,F"After major events that happened to
OL,19,Fhim, twice I had to get counselling
OL,20,Fand it still haunts me.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
