PN,41404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1781866972
OL,3,CFamilies speak out about loved ones'
OL,4,Ctreatment as Muckamore report published
OL,6,F"My life is overshadowed by the fact
OL,7,Fthat he ever was at Muckamore", he
OL,8,Ftold UTV.
OL,10,FDanny may never know what happened to
OL,11,Fhis son.
OL,13,FFor Glynn Brown, the evidence was
OL,14,Fthere all along.
OL,16,FHe suspected staff had assaulted his
OL,17,Fson Aaron, but was told there was 'no
OL,18,Fproof'.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/6
