PN,41405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1781866972
OL,3,CFamilies speak out about loved ones'
OL,4,Ctreatment as Muckamore report published
OL,6,FPolice later seized 300,000 hours of
OL,7,FCCTV footage revealing what the
OL,8,Finquiry heard was shocking abuse of
OL,9,Fvulnerable patients.
OL,11,F"It was hard to conceive that this was
OL,12,Fgoing on in a modern day NHS
OL,13,Fhospital", Mr Brown said.
OL,15,FMr Brown gathered and collated
OL,16,Fevidence to show that something wasn't
OL,17,Fright, he likened the process to"
OL,18,Fgetting blood out of a stone".
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
