OL,3,CFamilies speak out about loved ones'
OL,4,Ctreatment as Muckamore report published
OL,6,FAhead of the report's publication,
OL,7,FInquiry Chair Tom Kark KC met shared
OL,8,Fthe findings with the families and
OL,9,Fpraised them for their courage
OL,10,Ffighting for their loved ones.
OL,12,F"While the publication of this report
OL,13,Fcannot undo the harm suffered, it is
OL,14,Fmy hope that it will serve as a
OL,15,Fturning point", he said.
